  "title": "Packaging Notebooks for Production Using FastAPI with Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates how to transform Jupyter Notebooks into production-ready applications using FastAPI and Python 3.12+. The process includes converting the notebook to a Python script, setting up a virtual environment, installing required dependencies, writing an entry point, and deploying the application.",
